These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk, sprite, tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, photography, camping, drawing, rock-climbing, singing, baking
House: cottage, tower, palace, colonial, townhouse, modern, craftsman
7 different pets are kept: frog, pony, rabbit, bird, chinchilla, ferret, turtle
 1. the colonial house is on the far right##1
 2. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the palace house##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is the palace house##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
11. the cottage house is the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the frog##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
14. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the rabbit##1
15. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
16. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
17. the modern house is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
18. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
19. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | sprite        | soy-milk | fanta      | juice     | 7up      | tea     |
| Hobby   | photography | drawing         | baking   | dancing | singing    | rock-climbing | camping |
| House         | palace | townhouse | cottage | tower | craftsman  | modern  | colonial    |
| Pet     | chinchilla  | ferret         | frog     | pony    | rabbit | bird     | turtle     |

